Orlando Safe City is web app that allows those who are planning to move to orlando to find the safest neighborhood for them. Users are prompted to enter in an address which connects to google maps and plots all crimes in the area.
Newbie Tutor is an online web app designed to connect tutors with students seeking skills in the tech industry. After filling out a basic survey, the user is given a list of other users who may have the skills they're seeking.
The GIPHY App is a web application that connects to the giphy api and allows users to curate their own collection of gifs.
